1. charAt(index): This helps us in getting the character at any given index
2. indexOf(char): This helps us in getting the index of any given character
3. toUpper()    : Will convert your string to upper case
4. toLower()    : Will convert your string to lower case
5. trim()       : this replaces the space only at the beginning of the string and not at the end or in between
6. replace(old character, new character): Replaces old character with new one
7. contains()   : This checks the  existence of mentioned character sequence
8.